# Specs / Design Docs (Local Brain)

When writing a brainstorming spec or design document:

1. Resolve **`$BRAIN_PATH`** from `~/ai-dotfiles/config/brain.env` if unset.
2. Write the spec to:

   `$BRAIN_PATH/inbox/daily/specs/<project-name>/YYYY-MM-DD-<topic>-design.md`

3. Do **not** write specs inside the project repo (e.g. `docs/superpowers/specs/`).
